main event: A witness observed a UFO resembling three triangles in the sky during a sighting at Stone Harbor, New Jersey.
interesting points: The object was described as pale pink in the distance and amber when observed closely., The sighting lasted for about 15 minutes., The object was observed on a clear night with some clouds., There was no discernible sound from the object., The object reportedly disappeared behind a cloud during the sighting.
sighted object: one object resembling three triangles in the sky
